"{\n  \"text\": \"Hey everybody, I'm Scotty, the owner of Scotty's Fermented Foods. I'm a fermented food company, and this is my green apple sauerkraut. That's something I came up with myself because I know that sauerkraut's often served with apples. I decided to put them all together in one. This is not sweet. Anytime you ferment something, the natural sugars are robbed out of it by the bacteria. That's what they consume. That's why things become sour after you ferment them. So this is actually the most sour sauerkraut I do. It's not over the top, but it is sour. It's delicious. It's one of my very favorites. I think it goes well with savory items. And if you can, please order from me online and repost this video and help me share it. Comment, do any sort of interaction you can with this video. I would really appreciate it. Again, the green apple sauerkraut is what I'm trying to push today. You can order everything on Scottysfoods.com and any four items get you free shipping. I'm trying to make a big push towards online sales, and I really appreciate it. Thanks a lot, y'all.\",\n  \"sentences\": [\n    {\n      \"text\": \" Hey everybody, I'm Scotty, the owner of Scotty's Fermented Foods.\",\n      \"start\": 0.16,\n      \"end\": 3.2,\n      \"duration\": 3.04,\n      \"confidence\": 0.993,\n      \"tokens\": [\n        {\n          \"text\": \" He\",\n          \"start\": 0.16,\n          \"end\": 0.32,\n          \"duration\": 0.16,\n          \"confidence\": 0.976\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \"y\",\n          \"start\": 0.32,\n          \"end\": 0.4,\n          \"duration\": 0.08,\n          \"confidence\": 0.999\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \" ever\",\n          \"start\": 0.48,\n          \"end\": 0.56,\n          \"duration\": 0.08,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \"yb\",\n          \"start\": 0.56,\n          \"end\": 0.64,\n          \"duration\": 0.08,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0